er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9a%2FThe_Nice_Guys_Poster.jpg&h=0a71ff6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事改編自真人真事，敘述在2007年&ndash;2008年環球金融危機期間，四位以專業手法操作著金融業而進行大賣空、就此獲利的驚人事蹟<br />\n<br />\n2.故事設定於1970年代的洛杉磯，敘述私家偵探侯藍&middot;馬奇（雷恩&middot;葛斯林 飾）受到了脾氣控管不佳的暴力拳擊手傑克森&middot;希利（羅素&middot;克洛 飾）的聘請合作找出失蹤的少女艾蜜莉亞（瑪格麗特&middot;庫利 飾），但在過程中卻又捲入的色情片女星的離奇死亡案件中。在經過調查後，兩人發現一個令人震驚的犯罪陰謀正在醞釀之中<br />\n<br />\n12 25AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=czK%2FpXY%2BwmSUs%2FbpWp5dOZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d82a76e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=czK%2FpXY%2BwmSUs%2FbpWp5dOZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=6e130c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b664c0a3268210603d2fd21151ae3a1570a1812","tid":832313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e44ca38f199c84e51df5450b4490bbec468891","tid":832313,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},